column2: Ice out 4/22/93. first reading after ice out.
Calm wind- bright sun- temp. 60 degrees.
Sunny- air temp 59- lake depth test area 26 ft.- calm water- some algal blooms.
Partly sunny- air temp 70- calm weather- some algae blooms
Moderate winds- heavy overcast- air temp 80
Cloudy- air temp 61- drizzle- calm water- some algae blooms.  Lake level: very high
Sunny- air temp 66- test area depth 25 ft- calm water- floating algae mats
Sunny- air temp 68- test area depth 24 ft- calm water- lots of algal blooms
Sunny- air temp 79- test area depth 26 ft- calm water- lots of algae and weed growth- bad runoff problem.  Lake level: very high
Cloudy- temp is 70 degrees- test area depth is 25 ft- water is calm- algae level is very high- worse I've seen since 1983.
Cloudy- temp is 68 degrees- test area depth is 24 ft- water is fairly calm.  Algae level- is bad- bad- most algae mats.
Windy- temp is 75 degrees- test area is 25 ft deep.  Water is fairly calm- algae level is high.
Water is calm- temp is 80 degrees- test area is 26 ft- many algae mats.
Sunny- temp is 80 degrees- test area depth is 26 ft- water is calm- algal mats are bad- weeds are bad.
Overcast- windy- cold- 20' of ice on the lake edge- 34 degrees.
Sunny- calm- temp. 63 degrees.  Lake depth test area 23'.  Slight algae on water surface.  Weed growth just beginning.
Sunny- windy.  Temp. 65 degrees.  Test area 24'.  Algae on water surface- weeds growing.  Lake level down slightly.
Sunny- calm- temp. 72 degrees.  Test area 23'.  Weed growing rapidly.  Increase of algae on water surface.
Sunny- windy- temp. 85 degrees.  Test area 25'.  Algae blooms bad- weeds growing rapidly.
Lake choppy- temp. 78 degrees.  Test area 26'.  Algae + weed growth bad.  Lake Level: Way below normal
Sunny- temp. 82 degrees- calm.  Test area 25'.  Weeds + algae in full growth.  Lake Level: Way below normal
Cloudy- rained ~2 hours ago.  Temp. 74 degrees.  Test area 25'.  Weeds + algae bad around lake edges.  Lake Level: Way below normal
Cloudy- windy- temp. 78 degrees.  Test area 24'.  Weed growth bad around lake edges + in bays.
Cloudy- lake calm- temp. 75 degrees.  Test area 24'.  Weed growth bad around lake edges + in bays.
Sunny- lake calm- temp. 72 degrees.  Test area 25'.  Weed growth bad along shorelines.
Cloudy- lake calm- test area 27'.  Weeds + algae bad along shoe lines.
Sunny- lake calm- temp. 78 degrees.  Test area 25'.  Weedy along shorelines.
Beautiful- blue sky- minimal clouds- and the temperature is 70 degrees.
Sunny- lake choppy- test area is 24'- and the temperature is 80 degrees.  Weedy along shorelines and algae blooms floating.
Partly cloudy- lake calm- temp. 75 degrees- test area 24'.  Some algal blooms- weedy along shorelines.
Partly cloudy- lake choppy- temp. 56 degrees- test area 26'- weeds along shoreline.
Sunny- temp. 69- test area 26'- lake calm- weedy shorelines.
Clear blue sky- light breeze- and the temperature is 75 degrees.
Sunny- lake calm- temperature is 70 degrees- test area is 26'- weedy shorelines- and some algal blooms.
Sunny- temp. 71 degrees.  Test area depth 27'.  Bad algae mats.  Bad algae and weeds along shorelines.

Sunny- temp. 72 degrees- test area 27'-many floating algae mats along shoreline.  Weeds also a big problem along shorelines-middle of lake cleared off of algae mats.  Lake level: Way below normal- calm
Cloudy- temp 72 degrees- test area 25'- lake calm- algae + weeds along shorelines.  Weeds and lily pads coming up all over.
Test area 24'.  Lake semi-calm- temp. 89 degrees- sunny- weeds and algae plentiful along shorelines.  Weeds + pads up in force-water very low.
Hot- sunny- light wind- 90 degree temp. No clouds- water is very clear- but with slight green tinge to it.
Test area 25'- calm- temp. 83 degrees-sunny- heavy weeds and algae blooms- lake water extremely low- weedy shorelines.
Test area 26.5'- temp 77 degrees- calm- extreme growth of lily pads- algae blooms- weed blooms let loose from bottom of lake-now floating on lake surface- cloudy.
Test area 25.75'- sunny- temp. 83 degrees- calm- still many algae blooms- weedy shorelines- bad duckweed areas- floating bullrushes.  Water level: very low.
Lake calm- temp. 80 degrees- sunny- test area 26.5'- algae plentiful- middle of lake clear- shoreline weeds and duck weed.  Water level: very low.
Temp. 80- lake calm- sunny- test area 26.5'- weedy- algae plentiful- shorelines very weedy- lots of duckweed.  Water level: very low.
Temp. 75 degrees- sunny- test area 24'- lake calm- algae- weeds- duck weed and algae floats.  Contributing to aesthetic enjoyment of lake and swimming.  Water level: Very low
Temp. 80 degrees- sunny- test area 25'- calm- shorelines overrun by weeds- algae mats and blooms.  Water level: very low.
Lake calm- temp. 75 degrees- sunny- test area 24.5'.  Shorelines extremely bad with weeds- lily pads- algae blooms- and duckweed.  Water level: Very low-down 6"
Lake calm.  Temp. 83 degrees- sunny- test area 25.5'.  Weeds + pads bad- algae 7 duckweed accumulation along shorelines.
Partly cloudy- temp. 48 degrees- lake calm- test area 24.5'- weeds + pads bad- heavy duckweed along shorelines from heavy rains.
Sunny- temp. 81 degrees- lake calm- test area 25.5'.  Weeds + pads still bad- few algae mats- still heavy duckweed along shorelines.
Cool- 52 degrees- partly cloudy- windy.  Bottom sample- no depth reported- assumed 20'.
Sunny- temp. 60 degrees- test area 24'- lake calm- algae along shoreline- lily pads starting to grow.
Windy- partly cloudy- 78 degrees.  Slight scum on lake surface.
Partly sunny- temp. 70 degrees- lake calm- test area 27'- some duckweed- and a few algal mats.
Partly sunny- 76 degrees- lake calm- test area 25'- some algae mats- duckweed growing.
Sunny- 88 degrees- lake calm- test area 28'- algae mats getting more plentiful- more duckweed is showing up along shorelines.
Partly sunny- 78 degrees- lake calm- test area 26'- many algal mats- lily pads plentiful in some areas- duckweed along shorelines.
Cloudy- 70 degrees- lake fairly calm- test area 25'. weed blooms let loose from bottom of lake. dead floating bullrushes- duckweed along shoreline- algal mats still present.
Lake calm- sunny- temp. 77 degrees- test area 25'. floating blooms- algae mats- duck weed along shoreline- lots of lily pads.
Clear blue sky- temp is 75 degrees- light breeze.
Lake calm- sunny- temp. 75 degrees- test area 25'. duckweed and algae along shoreline. floating dead bullrushes.
Sunny- temp 74 degrees- lake calm- test area 26.5'. algae- blooms- duckweed. some bulrushes all floating on water. many lily pads.
Sunny- temp. 72 degrees- lake calm- test area 27'. algae- buckweed- weed blooms + masses- all floating on surface of water- very weedy along shorelines.
Lake calm- temp. 70 degrees- sunny- test area 25'. algae- duckweed- weed blooms- and lily pads floating on surface of water.
Lake calm. temp. 75 degrees- sunny- test area 25'. algae and blooms on lake surface.
Lake-bad under tow. sunny- temp. 72 degrees- lake calm- test area 25'- mixture of weeds and algae on lake surface.
Sunny- 80 degrees- lake calm- test area 27'- shoreline overrun with weeds- algae blooms and duckweed.
Sunny- temp. 62 degrees- lake calm- test area 26'- shoreline weedy with lots of chara blooms and lily pads.  Lake Level: Way above average-due to 4" of rain received on 9-4-96
Sunny.  Lake calm.  Temperature 74 degrees. test area 25 1/5 feet.  Algae bloom on surface.  Weedy along the shoreline.
Sunny and calm.  71 degrees- test area = 27 feet.  Algae blooms- mixture of weeds and algae on surface of lake.
Greenish-brown.  Sunny - temperature 82 degrees.  Test area 27 feet.  Algae blooms on lake.  Very weed along shoreline.  Duckweed starting up.
Greenish brown.  Partly sunny.  Temperature 80 degrees.  26 feet is the test area.  Algae and duckweed on lake surface.  Lily pads are growing.  Dead bull rush on lake surface.
Temperature 69 degrees.  Test area is 26 feet.  Algae level bad.  Weedy around shoreline.  Duckweed and lily pads growing rapidly.
Sunny- temperature 73 degrees.  Test area 25 feet.  Algae and weed level plentiful.  Duckweed plentiful.
Greenish brown water.  Sunny.  Temperature of 72 degrees.  Test area 27 feet.  Algae mats and lily pads.  Good swimming in the center of the lake- impossible around edges.
Greenish brown. partly sunny- 74 degrees  test area 24 feet.  Weedy shorelines- still some chara blooms floating.  Duckweed plentiful.
Greenish brown water.  Sunny- temperature 78 degrees.  Test area 251/2 feet.  Algae and weeds bad along the shoreline.  Middle of lake is clear.
Sunny.  Temperature 80 degrees.  Test area 27 1/2 feet.  Duckweed- algae and small weed mats along the shoreline.  Weeds in full growth.
Sunny.  Temperature 70 degrees.  Test area 25 feet.  Lake clear in the middle- weedy and duckweed along the shore.
Sunny. temperature 74 degrees.  Test area=24 feet.  Algae and weeds along shoreline.  Lily pads plentiful.
Temperature 74 degrees.  Test area 25 feet.  Algae and weeds plentiful.  Lily pads are also plentiful.  Bad weed year.
